node.text:
Paul Costabile discovers the roots of the popular Instagram account and magazine, “Boys with Plants.”

Featured: 
New York Live @newyorklivetv
Paul Costabile @paulcostabile
Scott Cain @tropicaloco 
Lorenzo Edwards @lorenzoedwards__ 

#boyswithplants #boyswithplantsmagazine
